query:
SELECT p.id, p.serviceId, p.countryId, p.apiId, p.ourPrice, p.quantityAvailable, s.smshubCode, c.name as countryName, a.name as apiName
FROM prices p
JOIN services s ON p.serviceId = s.id
JOIN countries c ON p.countryId = c.id
LEFT JOIN sms_apis a ON p.apiId = a.id
WHERE s.smshubCode = 'wa'
ORDER BY p.apiId
